{"tid":166272,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"係澳洲考車牌 有咩要注意？","createTime":"2017-03-22T03:56:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-23T13:14:52.000Z","uid":25646,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8fdf5550dd33178db8b02f6472b3b0a963df505d","tid":166272,"uid":25646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T03:56:35.000Z","msg":"由於係香港唔夠時間排期考車 就過左澳洲WH<br />\n但發現冇車做農場 真係好慘<br />\n黎緊會去考筆試先攞L牌 因為唔夠25歲 （仲有幾個月先夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n但係等到25歲我都夠鐘返香港<br />\n想問下 有冇巴絲係澳洲考過車牌 有咩特別要注意？"},{"pid":"9d3bc1d28b3deeb62d52ce3934f55203838af703","tid":166272,"uid":55601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T04:02:18.000Z","msg":"小心駕駛"},{"pid":"6fe050b39b26993406c8edff8b416eb74357cd71","tid":166272,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T04:14:41.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"b7cbb7ee9237aa59d9cf424f76330af630eee726","tid":166272,"uid":8963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T08:05:16.000Z","msg":"你係澳洲咩state?<br />\n考完learner 你分分鐘都冇時間攞P牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d231269a5d1da27239d41678a206a00e94fee883","tid":166272,"uid":4703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T08:38:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係澳洲咩state?<br />\n考完learner 你分分鐘都冇時間攞P牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nHi 巴打認唔認得我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2276c73b81108fec497b245642d2be543cbf716f","tid":166272,"uid":4703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T08:39:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由於係香港唔夠時間排期考車 就過左澳洲WH<br />\n但發現冇車做農場 真係好慘<br />\n黎緊會去考筆試先攞L牌 因為唔夠25歲 （仲有幾個月先夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n但係等到25歲我都夠鐘返香港<br />\n想問下 有冇巴絲係澳洲考過車牌 有咩特別要注意？</blockquote><br />\n真心得幾個月時間真係廢事搞將就下返到香港先考啦"},{"pid":"40f33441d96cd2d2c482b39100725ba33a09331e","tid":166272,"uid":8963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T08:46:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你係澳洲咩state?<br />\n考完learner 你分分鐘都冇時間攞P牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nHi 巴打認唔認得我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打保險搞成點？"},{"pid":"4037a2939239b994c4e37a207f28e6e3cc824db5","tid":166272,"uid":25646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T11:50:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係澳洲咩state?<br />\n考完learner 你分分鐘都冇時間攞P牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係QLD <br />\n集緊二簽 十一月會返一返香港再返澳洲"},{"pid":"37efb841434a6997a35d94ec1d8e3e12d53c75bb","tid":166272,"uid":25646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T11:53:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>由於係香港唔夠時間排期考車 就過左澳洲WH<br />\n但發現冇車做農場 真係好慘<br />\n黎緊會去考筆試先攞L牌 因為唔夠25歲 （仲有幾個月先夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n但係等到25歲我都夠鐘返香港<br />\n想問下 有冇巴絲係澳洲考過車牌 有咩特別要注意？</blockquote><br />\n真心得幾個月時間真係廢事搞將就下返到香港先考啦</blockquote><br />\n因為集緊二簽 會再返黎 <br />\n同埋日日求人載真係好煩 所以想快啲考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加上係香港考貴好多"},{"pid":"754a46c99d424c111a07f7009c49fb43ff53b5c1","tid":166272,"uid":4703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T15:49:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你係澳洲咩state?<br />\n考完learner 你分分鐘都冇時間攞P牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nHi 巴打認唔認得我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打保險搞成點？</blockquote><br />\n唔該哂你呀巴打 我已經買左suncorp啦 雖然好肉赤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85a18f794eb6eb9c7d9383fd62a5487ef28e9209","tid":166272,"uid":4703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T15:52:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你係澳洲咩state?<br />\n考完learner 你分分鐘都冇時間攞P牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係QLD <br />\n集緊二簽 十一月會返一返香港再返澳洲</blockquote><br />\n係Brisbane? 如果我係你我會等到25歲先報考L<br />\n如果無記錯既話因為25歲打後L完一揸夠100個鐘（under instruction）就可以即考路試唔洗等1年先考到（only in QLD)"},{"pid":"19aa1ebc26ebb58f1b597784e4b94d56e8258dd5","tid":166272,"uid":8963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T23:33:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你係澳洲咩state?<br />\n考完learner 你分分鐘都冇時間攞P牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係QLD <br />\n集緊二簽 十一月會返一返香港再返澳洲</blockquote><br />\n係Brisbane? 如果我係你我會等到25歲先報考L<br />\n如果無記錯既話因為25歲打後L完一揸夠100個鐘（under instruction）就可以即考路試唔洗等1年先考到（only in QLD)</blockquote><br />\n個100個鐘你要跟師傅學唔可以自己揸"},{"pid":"2ce63cf0a30e5e758f908703e8ab62499a742708","tid":166272,"uid":8963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T23:33:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你係澳洲咩state?<br />\n考完learner 你分分鐘都冇時間攞P牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nHi 巴打認唔認得我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打保險搞成點？</blockquote><br />\n唔該哂你呀巴打 我已經買左suncorp啦 雖然好肉赤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最後出左咩車？"},{"pid":"7985e789e93a52d0e517c0a10e48b355795b09e9","tid":166272,"uid":8963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T23:35:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你係澳洲咩state?<br />\n考完learner 你分分鐘都冇時間攞P牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係QLD <br />\n集緊二簽 十一月會返一返香港再返澳洲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做咩咁傻唔係香港考完牌先黎澳洲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01cb41cf007a50fb33b346d48c4d6bd2078588ae","tid":166272,"uid":2346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T23:58:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你係澳洲咩state?<br />\n考完learner 你分分鐘都冇時間攞P牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係QLD <br />\n集緊二簽 十一月會返一返香港再返澳洲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做咩咁傻唔係香港考完牌先黎澳洲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n澳洲考牌同玩自己差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb8b5b1c01a083d948c39918727d703cdc2648a9","tid":166272,"uid":8963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T01:24:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你係澳洲咩state?<br />\n考完learner 你分分鐘都冇時間攞P牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係QLD <br />\n集緊二簽 十一月會返一返香港再返澳洲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做咩咁傻唔係香港考完牌先黎澳洲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n澳洲考牌同玩自己差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又唔係玩自己嘅，係對working holiday 嘅人好仆街啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc51a6b427582775d5625ddcd6fec37fd9bc7a65","tid":166272,"uid":4703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T08:40:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你係澳洲咩state?<br />\n考完learner 你分分鐘都冇時間攞P牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係QLD <br />\n集緊二簽 十一月會返一返香港再返澳洲</blockquote><br />\n係Brisbane? 如果我係你我會等到25歲先報考L<br />\n如果無記錯既話因為25歲打後L完一揸夠100個鐘（under instruction）就可以即考路試唔洗等1年先考到（only in QLD)</blockquote><br />\n個100個鐘你要跟師傅學唔可以自己揸</blockquote><br />\n啱呀 嗰100個鐘裏面頭10個鐘跟師傅學的話個鐘數有得乘3倍（qld規則）<br />\n即係最少都要額外再揸夠70個鐘<br />\n而依70個鐘你隔離要坐個1年以上澳洲open driver licence既朋友幫你簽鐘先可以上路 <br />\n所以夾夾埋埋最少都要學夠in total 80個鐘先可以去考牌<br />\nDetail 自己睇transportation department 上面講嘅只係比你參考 唔可以作準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f37a556e9e31861e5e5e343502c20804b1850d38","tid":166272,"uid":4703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T08:43:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你係澳洲咩state?<br />\n考完learner 你分分鐘都冇時間攞P牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nHi 巴打認唔認得我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打保險搞成點？</blockquote><br />\n唔該哂你呀巴打 我已經買左suncorp啦 雖然好肉赤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最後出左咩車？</blockquote><br />\n13年Corolla sport <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鍾意掃把佬但我新牌仔技術未夠唔敢揸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過澳洲揸車真係好爽 嚟左一個月我已經揸左2千2km百<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"302d5449de0b699d0a089d8669d2b8899347ee62","tid":166272,"uid":4703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T08:46:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>由於係香港唔夠時間排期考車 就過左澳洲WH<br />\n但發現冇車做農場 真係好慘<br />\n黎緊會去考筆試先攞L牌 因為唔夠25歲 （仲有幾個月先夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n但係等到25歲我都夠鐘返香港<br />\n想問下 有冇巴絲係澳洲考過車牌 有咩特別要注意？</blockquote><br />\n真心得幾個月時間真係廢事搞將就下返到香港先考啦</blockquote><br />\n因為集緊二簽 會再返黎 <br />\n同埋日日求人載真係好煩 所以想快啲考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加上係香港考貴好多</blockquote><br />\n老實講香港唔會太貴嘅 我學車連埋考都係比左6千鬆啲 睇返依邊個學車價都at least 50幾per lesson同香港差唔多"},{"pid":"98afaae9dd3f893e729f35ae42ee2bd0a074b5c5","tid":166272,"uid":66680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T08:48:36.000Z","msg":"澳洲考車牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  買車牌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75712d51a1b0baf1eeefeae14b7aa6a4024095dd","tid":166272,"uid":4703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T08:50:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>澳洲考車牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  買車牌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪害人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0784f29f414978156f131673c283df48bcd7890a","tid":166272,"uid":3914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T08:52:05.000Z","msg":"要等一年先上到P牌真係好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b07683b08e7dc8131d476e7e46d642680e7f79e3","tid":166272,"uid":8963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T08:52:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>澳洲考車牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  買車牌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n知唔知年中有幾多working holiday 冇牌駕駛撞死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e9fb77cca0153f5493dec0271badd5567755024","tid":166272,"uid":8963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T08:53:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你係澳洲咩state?<br />\n考完learner 你分分鐘都冇時間攞P牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nHi 巴打認唔認得我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打保險搞成點？</blockquote><br />\n唔該哂你呀巴打 我